reviewText: the best wedding og the year
OMG... i love the part where dela Rosa nd Lim damily sings... to the seller i rcvd the items so fast ...
The delivery was fast and efficient. The DVD is of good quality, although I have to mark my star rating down as the casing arrived broken ;-((.
It is okay at first but when I played it again it will not work. Maybe the disc has a problem . I want to return it if it is okay and change it with a new one.

If you are planning to buy just one DVD on the series, this is the one.  For a lot of fans of the series, this was the highlight of the show.  It covers all the episodes that deal with the wedding of Maya and Ser Chief.  Watch it and have a keepsake.
